pokedexEntries.gold: If you are burned by the flames it shoots from its mouth, the pain will never go away.
pokedexEntries.silver: Upon hearing its eerie howls, other Pokémon get the shivers and head straight back to their nests.
pokedexEntries.crystal: The pungent-smelling flame that shoots from its mouth results from toxins burning in its body.
pokedexEntries.ruby: In a Houndoom pack, the one with its horns raked sharply towards the back serves a leadership role. These Pokémon choose their leader by fighting amongst themselves.

pokedexEntries.ultraSun: They spew flames mixed with poison to finish off their opponents. They divvy up their prey evenly among the members of their pack.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: Identifiable by its eerie howls, people a long time ago thought it was the grim reaper and feared it.
